      {
        title: 'Real-time Market Data',
        description:
          'It shows what is trending right now across stores and products, so you can see fast changes in demand and buying behavior. This helps users catch early opportunities before they become mainstream.',
        icon: 'tabler:brand-tailwind',
      },
      {
        title: 'Ad Creative Insights',
        description:
          'You can explore high-performing ads and creative formats that are currently running in different niches. It helps users understand which hooks, visuals, and messages are driving conversions.',
        icon: 'tabler:components',
      },
      {
        title: 'Store Performance Tracking',
        description:
          'The tool lets you analyze successful online stores, including traffic trends and growth patterns. It makes competitor research more structured and easier to act on.',
        icon: 'tabler:list-check',
      },
      {
        title: 'Product Discovery Engine',
