        title: 'Competitor Strategy View',
        description:
          'Users can study how other brands structure their funnels, pricing, and acquisition strategies, giving a clearer picture of how top players operate.',
        icon: 'tabler:arrows-right-left',
      },
      {
        title: 'Flexible & Trusted Intelligence',
        description:
          'A consolidated platform replaces multiple disjointed spying subscriptions. Apply your verified TrendTrack Promo Code WINNING to minimize your tool stack expenses.',
        icon: 'tabler:bulb',
